* Microsoft COBOL Version 4.5        L2.4 revision 002 27-May-25 21:42 Page   1
*                                      EXERC7.CBL
* Options: LIST(EXERC7.LST) ASMLIST(EXERC7.GRP)
     1 IDENTIFICATION    DIVISION.
     2 PROGRAM-ID.    EXERC7.
     3 AUTHOR.        YHAGO.
     4 INSTALLATION.    FATEC-SP.
     5 DATE-WRITTEN.    27/05/2025.
     6 DATE-COMPILED. 27-May-25 21:42.
     7 SECURITY.    APENAS O AUTOR PODE MODIFICAR.
     8
     9 ENVIRONMENT    DIVISION.
    10 CONFIGURATION    SECTION.
    11 SOURCE-COMPUTER.    MY-PC.
    12 OBJECT-COMPUTER.    MY-PC.
    13 SPECIAL-NAMES.    DECIMAL-POINT IS COMMA.
    14
    15 INPUT-OUTPUT     SECTION.
    16 FILE-CONTROL.
    17     SELECT CADALU ASSIGN TO DISK
    18             ORGANIZATION IS LINE SEQUENTIAL.
    19     SELECT ARQ-SORT ASSIGN TO DISK.
    20     SELECT RELALU ASSIGN TO DISK.
    21
    22 DATA    DIVISION.
    23 FILE    SECTION.
    24 FD CADALU
    25     LABEL RECORD STANDARD
    26     VALUE OF FILE-ID IS "CADENT.DAT".
    27 01 REG-ENTRADA.
    28     02 TURMA-ENT         PIC 9(03).
    29     02 CODALUNO-ENT      PIC 9(07).
    30     02 NOMEALUNO-ENT     PIC X(30).
    31     02 NOTAS-ENT.
    32       03 NOTA1          PIC 99V99.
    33       03 NOTA2          PIC 99V99.
    34       03 NOTA3          PIC 99V99.
    35       03 NOTA4          PIC 99V99.
    36 SD ARQ-SORT .
    37 01 REG-SORT.
    38     02 TURMA-SORT         PIC 9(03).
    39     02 CODALUNO-SORT      PIC 9(07).
    40     02 NOMEALUNO-SORT     PIC X(30).
    41     02 MEDIA-SORT         PIC 99V99.
    42 FD RELALU
    43     LABEL RECORD  OMITTED.
    44 01 REG-ATR      PIC X(80).
    45 WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
    46     77 FIM-ARQ          PIC X(03) VALUE "NAO".
    47     77 CT-LIN           PIC 9(02) VALUE 40.
    48     77 CT-PAG           PIC 9(02) VALUE ZEROS.
    49     77 APROVADOS        PIC 9(03) VALUE ZEROS.
    50     77 REPROVADOS       PIC 9(03) VALUE ZEROS.
    51     77 MEDIA-GERAL      PIC 9(05)V9(02) VALUE ZEROS.
    52     77 TURMA            PIC 9(03) VALUE ZEROS.
    53 01 WHITE-CAB.
    54     02 FILLER     PIC X(80) VALUE SPACES.
    55 01 CAB-01.
    56     02 FILLER     PIC X(20) VALUE SPACES.
    57     02 FILLER     PIC X(17) VALUE "RELAÇĂO DE ALUNOS".
* Microsoft COBOL Version 4.5        L2.4 revision 002 27-May-25 21:42 Page   2
*                                      EXERC7.CBL
    58     02 FILLER     PIC X(15) VALUE SPACES.
    59     02 FILLER     PIC X(05) VALUE "PAG. ".
    60     02 VAR-PAG    PIC ZZ9.
    61 01 CAB-TURMA.
    62     02 FILLER     PIC X(07) VALUE "TURMA: ".
    63     02 VAR-TURMA  PIC 9(03).
    64
    65 01 CAB-02.
    66     02 FILLER     PIC X(06) VALUE "CÓDIGO".
    67     02 FILLER     PIC X(15) VALUE SPACES.
    68     02 FILLER     PIC X(04) VALUE "NOME".
    69     02 FILLER     PIC X(15) VALUE SPACES.
    70     02 FILLER     PIC X(05) VALUE "MEDIA".
    71 01 DETALHE.
    72     02 VAR-COD       PIC 9(07).
    73     02 FILLER        PIC X(05) VALUE SPACES.
    74     02 VAR-NOME      PIC X(30) .
    75     02 FILLER        PIC X(10) VALUE SPACES.
    76     02 VAR-MEDIA     PIC Z9,99.
    77
    78 01 RODAPE-APROVADOS.
    79     02 FILLER     PIC X(29)
    80         VALUE "TOTAL DE ALUNOS APROVADOS    ".
    81     02 ROD-APROVADOS  PIC Z9,99.
    82 01 RODAPE-REPROVADOS.
    83     02 FILLER     PIC X(29)
    84         VALUE "TOTAL DE ALUNOS REPROVADOS   ".
    85     02 ROD-REPROVADOS  PIC Z9,99.
    86 01 RODAPE-GERAL.
    87     02 FILLER     PIC X(29)
    88         VALUE "MEDIA GERAL                  ".
    89     02 ROD-MEDIA-GERAL  PIC Z9,99.
    90 PROCEDURE    DIVISION.
    91 PGM-EX05.
    92 SORT    ARQ-SORT
    93         ON ASCENDING KEY TURMA-SORT
    94         ON ASCENDING KEY CODALUNO-SORT
    95         INPUT PROCEDURE ROT-ENTRADA
    96         OUTPUT PROCEDURE ROT-RELATORIO.
    97
    98 STOP    RUN.
    99 ROT-ENTRADA SECTION.
   100     PERFORM INICIO-ENTRADA.
   101     PERFORM PRINCIPAL-ENTRADA
   102             UNTIL FIM-ARQ EQUAL "SIM".
   103     PERFORM FIM-ENTRADA.
   104 INICIO-ENTRADA SECTION.
   105     OPEN INPUT CADALU.
   106     PERFORM LEITURA-ENTRADA.
   107 LEITURA-ENTRADA SECTION.
   108        READ CADALU
   109          AT END MOVE "SIM" TO FIM-ARQ.
   110
   111 PRINCIPAL-ENTRADA SECTION.
   112     PERFORM MEDIA-ENTRADA.
   113     PERFORM GRAVACAO-ENTRADA.
   114     PERFORM LEITURA-ENTRADA.
   115
* Microsoft COBOL Version 4.5        L2.4 revision 002 27-May-25 21:42 Page   3
*                                      EXERC7.CBL
   116 MEDIA-ENTRADA SECTION.
   117  COMPUTE MEDIA-SORT = (NOTA1 + NOTA2 + NOTA3 + NOTA4) / 4.
   118
   119 GRAVACAO-ENTRADA SECTION.
   120 DISPLAY "VALORES PARA SORT:" REG-SORT.
   121        MOVE TURMA-ENT TO TURMA-SORT.
   122        MOVE CODALUNO-ENT TO CODALUNO-SORT.
   123        MOVE NOMEALUNO-ENT TO NOMEALUNO-SORT.
   124               DISPLAY "TURMA: " TURMA-SORT.
   125 DISPLAY "CODIGO: " CODALUNO-SORT.
   126 DISPLAY "NOME: " NOMEALUNO-SORT.
   127 DISPLAY "MEDIA: " MEDIA-SORT.
   128     RELEASE REG-SORT.
   129
   130 FIM-ENTRADA.
   131     CLOSE CADALU.
   132
   133 ROT-RELATORIO SECTION.
   134     PERFORM INICIO-SAIDA.
   135     PERFORM PRINCIPAL-SAIDA
   136             UNTIL FIM-ARQ EQUAL "SIM".
   137     PERFORM FIM-SAIDA.
   138
   139 INICIO-SAIDA SECTION.
   140     MOVE "NAO" TO FIM-ARQ.
   141     OPEN OUTPUT RELALU.
   142     PERFORM LEITURA-SAIDA.
   143
   144 LEITURA-SAIDA SECTION.
   145     RETURN ARQ-SORT
   146      AT END
   147      PERFORM RODAPE
   148      MOVE 'SIM' TO FIM-ARQ.
   149
   150 PRINCIPAL-SAIDA SECTION.
   151     PERFORM SELECAO-SAIDA.
   152     PERFORM LEITURA-SAIDA.
   153 SELECAO-SAIDA SECTION.
   154     IF MEDIA-SORT < 7
   155         ADD 1 TO REPROVADOS
   156     ELSE
   157         ADD 1 TO APROVADOS
   158     END-IF.
   159     PERFORM GRAVACAO-SAIDA.
   160 GRAVACAO-SAIDA SECTION.
   161     IF CT-LIN GREATER THAN 39
   162         PERFORM CABECALHO-01
   163     END-IF.
   164     IF NOT(TURMA-SORT = TURMA)
   165          PERFORM CABECALHO-02
   166     END-IF.
   167     MOVE TURMA-SORT TO TURMA.
   168     PERFORM DETALHES.
   169 CABECALHO-01   SECTION.
   170     ADD 1         TO CT-PAG.
   171     MOVE CT-PAG   TO VAR-PAG.
   172     MOVE SPACES   TO REG-ATR.
   173     WRITE REG-ATR AFTER ADVANCING PAGE.
* Microsoft COBOL Version 4.5        L2.4 revision 002 27-May-25 21:42 Page   4
*                                      EXERC7.CBL
   174     WRITE REG-ATR FROM CAB-01 AFTER ADVANCING 1 LINE.
   175     WRITE REG-ATR FROM WHITE-CAB AFTER ADVANCING 1 LINE.
   176     MOVE 2  TO CT-LIN.
   177 CABECALHO-02 SECTION.
   178     IF NOT(TURMA = ZEROS)
   179         MOVE TURMA-SORT TO VAR-TURMA
   180         MOVE APROVADOS TO ROD-APROVADOS
   181         MOVE REPROVADOS TO ROD-REPROVADOS
   182         COMPUTE
   183            MEDIA-GERAL = MEDIA-GERAL / (APROVADOS + REPROVADOS)
   184         MOVE MEDIA-GERAL TO ROD-MEDIA-GERAL
   185         WRITE REG-ATR FROM RODAPE-APROVADOS
   186             AFTER ADVANCING 2 LINE
   187         WRITE REG-ATR FROM RODAPE-REPROVADOS
   188             AFTER ADVANCING 1 LINE
   189         WRITE REG-ATR FROM RODAPE-GERAL
   190                AFTER ADVANCING 1 LINE
   191         MOVE ZEROS TO APROVADOS
   192         MOVE ZEROS TO REPROVADOS
   193         MOVE ZEROS TO MEDIA-GERAL
   194         PERFORM CABECALHO-01
   195         WRITE REG-ATR FROM CAB-TURMA
   196             AFTER ADVANCING 1 LINE
   197     ELSE
   198          WRITE REG-ATR FROM CAB-TURMA
   199             AFTER ADVANCING 1 LINE
   200     END-IF.
   201
   202 DETALHES SECTION.
   203     ADD MEDIA-SORT TO MEDIA-GERAL.
   204     MOVE CODALUNO-SORT TO VAR-COD.
   205     MOVE NOMEALUNO-SORT TO VAR-NOME.
   206     MOVE MEDIA-SORT TO VAR-MEDIA.
   207     WRITE REG-ATR FROM DETALHE AFTER ADVANCING 1 LINE.
   208 RODAPE SECTION.
   209     MOVE APROVADOS TO RODAPE-APROVADOS.
   210     MOVE REPROVADOS TO ROD-REPROVADOS.
   211     MOVE MEDIA-GERAL TO ROD-MEDIA-GERAL.
   212     WRITE REG-ATR FROM RODAPE-APROVADOS AFTER ADVANCING 2 LINE.
   213     WRITE REG-ATR FROM RODAPE-REPROVADOS AFTER ADVANCING 1 LINE.
   214     WRITE REG-ATR FROM RODAPE-GERAL AFTER ADVANCING 1 LINE.
   215
   216 FIM-SAIDA SECTION.
   217     CLOSE RELALU.
